            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "To provide a viable solution rather than just raising the issue, I believe we can first use `BufReadCmd` to implement this feature and treat any discrepancies between it and `nvim file` as known bugs. \n\nAn approach to resolving these discrepancies can be addressed later by changing the implementation method. For now, the practical issues caused by such known bugs appear to be minimal, and compared to the current netrw implementation, it does not actually cause a regression.",
